title: 2001 CAF Super Cup
text:
The 2001 CAF Super Cup was the ninth <a href="CAF%20Super%20Cup">CAF Super Cup</a>, an annual <a href="association%20football">football</a> match in <a href="Africa">Africa</a> organized by the <a href="Confederation%20of%20African%20Football">Confederation of African Football</a> (CAF), between the winners of the previous season's two CAF club competitions, the <a href="CAF%20Champions%20League">African Cup of Champions Clubs</a> and the <a href="African%20Cup%20Winners%27%20Cup">African Cup Winners' Cup</a>.
Match details.
